<inglise> Means </inglise>
<eesti> Vahendid </eesti>
<inglise> The Financial Instrument for Fisheries Guidance, hereafter referred to as "FIFG" may, under the conditions laid down in this Regulation, provide assistance for the measures defined in Titles II, III and IV within the fields covered by the common fisheries policy as defined in Article 1 of Regulation (EEC) No 3760/92. </inglise>
