<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The Commission Decision referred to in paragraph 1 shall fix, in particular, a series of objectives accompanied by a set of measures for their realisation, enabling management of fishing effort on an overall, long-term basis. </inglise>
