<inglise> (ii) by the total amount previously received in the case of aid for the temporary cessation of activities within the meaning of Article 16 (1) of this Regulation and under Article 14 of Regulation (EC) No 2468/98 paid during the year preceding permanent withdrawal or the setting up of the joint enterprise. </inglise>
