<inglise> Article 11 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 11 </eesti>
<inglise> Small-scale coastal fishing </inglise>
<eesti> V&auml;ikesemahuline rannap&uuml;&uuml;k </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of this Article, "small-scale coastal fishing" means fishing carried on by vessels of an overall length of less than 12 metres. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas artiklis t&auml;hendab "v&auml;ikesemahuline rannap&uuml;&uuml;k" kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki laevadega, mille kogupikkus on alla 12 meetri. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States may take additional measures as provided for under this Regulation to supplement the measures to improve the conditions in which small-scale coastal fishing is carried on, under the terms laid down in this Article. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid v&otilde;ivad vastavalt k&auml;esolevale m&auml;&auml;rusele v&otilde;tta k&auml;esolevas artiklis etten&auml;htud tingimustel t&auml;iendavaid meetmeid v&auml;ikesemahulise rannap&uuml;&uuml;gi tingimuste parandamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Where a group of owners of vessels or families of fishermen involved in small-scale coastal fisheries cooperatively implement an integrated collective project to develop or modernise this fishing activity, a lump-sum premium part-financed by the FIFG may be granted to the participants. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui v&auml;iksemahulise rannap&uuml;&uuml;giga tegelev laevaomanike r&uuml;hm v&otilde;i kaluripered rakendavad &uuml;hiselt integreeritud &uuml;hisprojekti, et arendada v&otilde;i moderniseerida k&otilde;nealust p&uuml;&uuml;gitegevust, v&otilde;ib projektis osalejatele anda FIFGi poolt osaliselt rahastatavat &uuml;hekordset h&uuml;vitist. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> The following projects, inter alia, may be considered integrated collective projects for the purpose of this paragraph: </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva l&otilde;ike t&auml;henduses v&otilde;ib integreeritud &uuml;hisprojektide hulka muu hulgas lugeda ka j&auml;rgmisi projekte: </eesti>
<inglise> - safety equipment on board and improvement of sanitary and working conditions, </inglise>
