<inglise> The measures taken under this Article may under no circumstances be invoked as contributing to the attainment of the objectives of the multiannual guidance programme referred to in Article 5, nor can they be justified by a recurrent seasonal suspension of activity as part of the ongoing management of fisheries. </inglise>
