<inglise> Age of vessels </inglise>
<eesti> Laevade vanus </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of this Regulation, the age of a vessel is a whole number defined as the difference between the year of the management authority's decision to grant a premium or aid and the year in which the vessel was built (or, if this is not known, the year of commissioning). </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses on laeva vanus t&auml;isarv, mis v&otilde;rdub korraldusasutuse poolt h&uuml;vitise v&otilde;i abi andmise otsuse aasta ja laeva ehitamise aasta (v&otilde;i kasutuselev&otilde;tmise aasta, kui ehitamise aasta ei ole teada) vahega. </eesti>
<inglise> 1.1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1.1. </eesti>
<inglise> Permanent withdrawal (Article 7(3)) </inglise>
<eesti> L&otilde;plik k&otilde;rvaldamine (artikli 7 l&otilde;ige 3) </eesti>
<inglise> (a) Permanent withdrawal may concern only vessels which have carried out a fishing activity for at least 75 days at sea in each of the two periods of 12 months preceding the date of the application for permanent withdrawal or, as the case may be, a fishing activity for at least 80 % of the number of days at sea permitted by current national regulations for the vessel concerned. </inglise>
<eesti> a) l&otilde;plikult k&otilde;rvaldatakse ainult need laevad, mis on merel kala p&uuml;&uuml;dnud v&auml;hemalt 75 p&auml;eva l&otilde;pliku k&otilde;rvaldamise taotlusele eelnenud kahe 12-kuulise ajavahemiku jooksul v&otilde;i vastavalt asjaoludele 80% kehtivate siseriiklike &otilde;igusnormidega lubatud merep&auml;evadest. </eesti>
<inglise> In the Baltic Sea the number of 75 days shall be reduced to: </inglise>
<eesti> L&auml;&auml;nemerel v&auml;hendatakse 75-p&auml;evast merep&auml;evade arvu: </eesti>
<inglise> - 60 for vessels registered in ports situated north of parallel 59&deg;30'N, </inglise>
<eesti> - 60 p&auml;evani laevade puhul, mis on registreeritud p&otilde;hja pool p&otilde;hjalaiusest 59&deg; 30' asuvates sadamates, </eesti>
<inglise> - 40 for vessels registered in ports situated north of parallel 59&deg;30'N and fishing for salmon; </inglise>
<eesti> - 40 p&auml;evani l&otilde;hep&uuml;&uuml;gilaevade puhul, mis on registreeritud p&otilde;hja pool p&otilde;hjalaiusest 59&deg; 30' asuvates sadamates; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) the following conditions must be met: </inglise>
<eesti> b) t&auml;idetud peavad olema j&auml;rgmised tingimused: </eesti>
<inglise> (i) prior to its permanent withdrawal, the vessel must be registered in the fishing vessel register of the Community; </inglise>
<eesti> i) enne l&otilde;plikku k&otilde;rvaldamist peab laev olema kantud &uuml;henduse kalalaevade registrisse; </eesti>
<inglise> (ii) the vessel must be operational at the time the decision is taken to grant the premium; </inglise>
<eesti> ii) h&uuml;vitise andmise otsuse tegemise ajal peab laev olema kasutusel; </eesti>
<inglise> (iii) after permanent withdrawal, the fishing licence must be cancelled and the vessel declared permanently deleted from the fishing vessel register of the Community; </inglise>
<eesti> iii) p&auml;rast l&otilde;plikku k&otilde;rvaldamist tuleb t&uuml;histada p&uuml;&uuml;gilitsents ning teatada laeva l&otilde;plikust kustutamisest &uuml;henduse kalalaevade registrist; </eesti>
<inglise> (iv) in the event of permanent transfer to a third country, the vessel must be registered in the register of the third country without delay and may never return to Community waters; </inglise>
<eesti> iv) laeva l&otilde;pliku &uuml;leandmise korral kolmandale riigile tuleb laev viivitamata kanda kolmanda riigi registrisse ning see ei tohi enam &uuml;henduse vetesse tagasi p&ouml;&ouml;rduda; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) if a vessel is lost between the date of the decision to grant the premium and the actual date of permanent withdrawal, the management authority shall make a financial correction for the amount of the compensation paid by the insurance; </inglise>
<eesti> c) kui laev kaotatakse h&uuml;vitise andmise otsuse kuup&auml;eva ja tegeliku l&otilde;pliku k&otilde;rvaldamise kuup&auml;eva vahelisel ajal, teeb korraldusasutus kindlustuse poolt makstavale kompensatsioonisummale vastava finantseerimiskorrektsiooni; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) no public aid within the meaning of Article 7 may be paid for a vessel transferred to a third country to replace a lost vessel belonging to a joint enterprise within the meaning of Article 8. </inglise>
<eesti> d) laevale, mis antakse &uuml;le kolmandale riigile, et asendada artiklis 8 m&auml;&auml;ratletud &uuml;hisettev&otilde;ttele kuuluvat kaotatud laeva, ei anta riigiabi artikli 7 t&auml;henduses. </eesti>
<inglise> 1.2. </inglise>
<eesti> 1.2. </eesti>
<inglise> Joint enterprises (Article 8) </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;hisettev&otilde;tted (artikkel 8) </eesti>
<inglise> (a) In addition to the conditions for the permanent transfer of a vessel to a third country within the meaning of Article 7(3) (b) and point 1.1 of this Annex, vessels, transferred within the framework of joint enterprises, must meet the following conditions: </inglise>
<eesti> a) peale laeva kolmandale riigile l&otilde;pliku &uuml;leandmise tingimuste artikli 7 l&otilde;ike 3 punkti b ja k&auml;esoleva lisa punkti 1.1 t&auml;henduses peavad &uuml;hisettev&otilde;tete raames &uuml;leantavad laevad vastama ka j&auml;rgmistele tingimustele: </eesti>
<inglise> (i) they must have been operating for at least the last five years, under the flag of a Member State of the Community: </inglise>
<eesti> i) laevad peavad olema olnud &uuml;henduse liikmesriigi lipu all kasutusel v&auml;hemalt viimased viis aastat: </eesti>
<inglise> - in Community waters, </inglise>
<eesti> - &uuml;henduse vetes, </eesti>
<inglise> - and/or in the waters of a third country either under a fisheries agreement with the Community or under another agreement, </inglise>
<eesti> - ja/v&otilde;i kolmanda riigi vetes kas &uuml;hendusega s&otilde;lmitud kalanduskokkuleppe v&otilde;i muu kokkuleppe alusel, </eesti>
<inglise> - and/or in international waters where fisheries are ruled by an international Convention; </inglise>
<eesti> - ja/v&otilde;i rahvusvahelistes vetes, kus kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki reguleeritakse rahvusvahelise konventsiooniga; </eesti>
