<inglise> (a) For the purpose of this Regulation, "inland fishing" means fisheries carried out for commercial purpose by vessels operating exclusively in inland waters of the territory of Member States and which are not subject to the provisions of Title II; </inglise>
<eesti> a) K&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses t&auml;hendab "kalap&uuml;&uuml;k sisevetel" kaubanduslikku kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki, mille puhul kasutatakse ainult liikmesriigi sisevetes tegutsevaid laevu ja mille suhtes ei kohaldata II jaotise s&auml;tteid; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) when the investment concerns the construction of a vessel for inland fishing, the provisions of point 1.3(a) of Annex III shall apply; </inglise>
<eesti> b) siseveep&uuml;&uuml;giks etten&auml;htud laeva ehitamist k&auml;sitleva investeeringu puhul kohaldatakse III lisa punkti 1.3 alapunkti a; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) when the investment concerns the modernisation of a vessel for inland fishing, the provisions of point 1.4(b) of Annex III shall apply; </inglise>
<eesti> c) siseveep&uuml;&uuml;giks kasutatava laeva moderniseerimist k&auml;sitleva investeeringu suhtes kohaldatakse III lisa punkti 1.4 alapunkti b; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) investments shall not be eligible for assistance if they are likely to jeopardise the equilibrium between the fleet size and the corresponding fish resources available; </inglise>
<eesti> d) abik&otilde;lblikeks ei loeta investeeringuid, mis t&otilde;en&auml;oliselt kahjustavad tasakaalu laevastiku suuruse ja vastavate olemasolevate kalavarude vahel; </eesti>
<inglise> (e) scrapping premiums for vessels for inland fishing shall not be eligible for assistance; </inglise>
<eesti> e) siseveep&uuml;&uuml;giks kasutatavate laevade vanametalliks lammutamise h&uuml;vitised ei ole abik&otilde;lblikud; </eesti>
<inglise> (f) the management authority shall take all necessary measures to ensure that vessels receiving financial assistance from the FIFG under Article 13 shall continue to operate exclusively in inland waters. </inglise>
<eesti> f) korraldusasutus v&otilde;tab k&otilde;ik vajalikud meetmed tagamaks, et artikli 13 kohaselt FIFGi rahalist abi saavad laevad j&auml;tkavad tegevust ainult sisevetel. </eesti>
